</a>

      
    </div>
  
  <div class="card-inset-details__body">

          <div class="card-inset-details__title">
        <a href="/us/blog/authenticity-for-the-win/202404/how-to-get-the-most-from-your-adhd-meds" title="How to Get the Most from Your ADHD Meds"> How to Get the Most from Your ADHD Meds </a>
      </div>
    
          <div class="card-inset-details__teaser-text">
        
            Fed up with ADHD meds? Before you break up, read this. 
      
      </div>
    
  </div>

</article>      </div>
    


  
          <div class="teaser--card-inset-details--row">
    

